text: - Speed is everything here at Annapurna.

It means delivering the
next generation of servers
for machine learning into the data center
and into the hands of the customers.
My name is Will Orr.
I'm a hardware development engineer
here in the Annapurna Labs
Machine Learning Acceleration team,
and so that really means
that I help design the circuit boards
that all of our chips go on
and where they go in the servers.
When I look at this board,

I think I probably see it
a little bit differently
than the average person.
There's some parts that I look at

and some memories of
some nights and weekends
when things didn't work the first time.
Some other parts that I look at

are memories of two
patents we have pending,

which is really cool,
it was a first for me,

and so that was a really
rewarding experience

from working on this,
but more than anything,

I'm just proud to know
that this is gonna be

in the AWS Data Center
for customers to use,
and that's a really cool feeling.
(bright music)
